OL,3,CWhen is my tip open over Christmas?
OL,4,CFull list of closures and opening times
OL,6,FTips across the Midlands are set to
OL,7,Fclose over the festive period, with
OL,8,Fcouncils announcing changed opening
OL,9,Ftimes during Christmas and the New
OL,10,FYear.
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency has said around
OL,13,F30% more waste is produced at this
OL,14,Ftime of the year compared to usual.
OL,16,FThis includes over one billion
OL,17,FChristmas cards which are thrown away
OL,18,Feach year.
