OL,3,CWhen is my tip open over Christmas?
OL,4,CFull list of closures and opening times
OL,6,FThe Department for Environment, Food &
OL,7,FRural Affairs estimates around 50,000
OL,8,Ftrees are cut down each year to make
OL,9,Fenough paper to wrap Christmas
OL,10,Fpresents.
OL,12,FCouncils across the Midlands have
OL,13,Furged residents to reduce waste
OL,14,Fwherever possible over the festive
OL,15,Fperiod, and to recycle where they can,
OL,16,Fusing 'household recycling centres'
OL,17,F(tips) if necessary.
